sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Benutzer
    participant System as System
    participant Server as Server

    User->>System: Initiate Video Call
    System->>Server: Establish Encrypted Connection
    Server-->>System: Connection Established
    System-->>User: Video Call Started
    User->>System: Send Video Stream
    System->>Server: Transmit Encrypted Video Stream
    Server-->>System: Stream Received
    System-->>User: Stream Acknowledged
    User->>System: End Video Call
    System->>Server: Terminate Connection
    Server-->>System: Connection Terminated
    System-->>User: Video Call Ended